{"title":"「TJOI2015」概率论","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["TJOI","2015"],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/1022#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=1022","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/1022/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/1022/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/1022"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"为了提高智商，ZJY 开始学习概率论。有一天，她想到了这样一个问题：\r\n\r\n对于一棵随机生成的 $n$ 个结点的有根二叉树（所有互相不同构的形态等概率出现），它的叶子节点数的期望是多少呢？\r\n\r\n判断两棵树是否同构的伪代码如下：\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/04/30/590588bc1af25.png\">"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入一个正整数 $N$，代表有根树的结点数"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出这棵树期望的叶子节点数。要求误差小于 $10^{-9}$"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n1\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n1.000000000\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq N \\leq 10^9$"}]}